text: West Calhoun is a neighborhood in Minneapolis, Minnesota. It is the southwesternmost neighborhood of the Calhoun Isles community in the western part of the city. West Calhoun is bordered on the east by East Calhoun, or "ECCO", the north by Cedar-Isles-Dean, the south by Linden Hills and the west by the city of St. Louis Park. Its boundaries are Lake Street to the north, Bde Maka Ska to the east, 36th Street to the south, and France Avenue to the west. ==References== ==External links== *Minneapolis Neighborhood Profile - West Calhoun Category:Neighborhoods in Minneapolis
